sentences.en: His statement ran athwart what was previously said.
sentences.cn: 他讲的话与先前所说的相抵触。

sentences.en: The contract was awarded to a previously unknown company.
sentences.cn: 该合同给了一家先前不知名的公司。

sentences.en: Guyana's railways were previously owned by private companies.
sentences.cn: 圭亚那的铁路先前为私营公司所拥有。
